# LDS Figma Make Themes

Custom theme for Figma Make based on the LDS Default Theme.

*Generated on 17/09/2025 using Figma Make UI Component Studio*

---

## Global Design Tokens

These foundational tokens should be applied at the root level of your application to maintain consistency across all components.

### Color Tokens

**CSS Custom Properties:**
```css
:root {
  --primary: #78DE1F;
  --primary-foreground: #003418;
  --secondary: #018444;
  --secondary-foreground: #FFFFFF;
  --background: #F2F2F2;
  --foreground: #4A4A4A;
  --card: #FFFFFF;
  --card-foreground: #4A4A4A;
  --muted: #F2F2F2;
  --muted-foreground: #6E6E6E;
  --accent: #F2F2F2;
  --accent-foreground: #030213;
  --destructive: #D92020;
  --destructive-foreground: #ffffff;
  --border: #E6E6E6;
}
```

### Typography Tokens

```css
:root {
  --font-size: 16px;
  --font-weight-normal: 400;
  --font-weight-medium: 500;
}

body {
  font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: var(--font-size);
}
```

### Border & Shape Tokens

```css
:root {
  --radius: 0.5rem;
}
```

### Spacing Tokens

```css
:root {
  --spacing-xs: 0.25rem;
  --spacing-sm: 0.5rem;
  --spacing-md: 1rem;
  --spacing-lg: 1.5rem;
  --spacing-xl: 2rem;
  --spacing-2xl: 3rem;
}
```

### Shadow Tokens

```css
:root {
  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
  --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
  --shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
}
```

